documentation.text: @dev Fallback function to handle ETH deposits
@dev Deposit ETH and receive WETH tokens

@dev Withdraw ETH by burning WETH tokens
 @param wad Amount of WETH to burn
@dev Get total supply (equals ETH locked in contract)

devdoc.details: Wrapped Ether (WETH) implementation This contract allows users to wrap ETH (deposit) and unwrap ETH (withdraw) It follows ERC20 standard for token operations

deposit().details: Deposit ETH and receive WETH tokens

totalSupply().details: Get total supply (equals ETH locked in contract)

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Transfer tokens from one address to another

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdraw ETH by burning WETH tokens
